# Read AGENTS.md first

`AGENTS.md` in the repo root is the single source of truth for this project —
architecture map, how to run/restart (it's a launchd service on port 5050),
conventions, and the CRITICAL GOTCHAS (launchd PATH/ffmpeg, ElevenLabs 120s
section cap, silent-generation-must-error, iOS native `<audio>` playback).

Multi-agent project (Claude Code, Cursor, Grok Build all edit this repo):
- One agent at a time; commit before switching tools; pull latest before starting.
- Commit messages are the shared log — write clear ones.
- Never commit secrets, `output/`, or `saved_jobs/`.
- After editing code, the launchd service must be restarted to take effect.
